{"tid":1057994,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"瘋傳開拍外語版《古惑仔》 劉偉強：我完全唔知情","createTime":"2019-03-12T08:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T13:26:27.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7d549158676caef54903eb89f9a711cda992e84c","tid":1057994,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:44:49.000Z","msg":"將本土文化電影的香港電影衝出國際，好似梁朝偉及劉德華主演《無間道》翻拍成《無間道風雲》、星爺主演《逃學威龍》被韓國翻拍為《逃學威鳳》等，今日大陸報道瘋傳導演劉偉強將拍攝英文版古惑仔。<br />\n<br />\n據大陸報道引述外媒Deadline報道指導演劉偉強計劃拍外語版《古惑仔》，與英國影業Pulse Film合作，講陳浩南崛起的故事，聲稱Thomas Benski、Dimitra Tsingou和Brian Levy做製作人，而劉偉強及Andrew Loo也會參與。<br />\n<br />\n不過，劉偉強今日接受《蘋果》查詢，他強調並無此事：「根本冇咁嘅事，我完全唔知情，唔知點解會出現呢啲新聞，唔該幫我澄清吓。」<br />\n<br />\n《古惑仔》以三合會為主題，於1992年開始連載，講述主角陳浩南在洪興社的故事，表達兄弟之情和江湖義氣，當時主演鄭伊健及黎姿在街上被叫「南哥」及「阿嫂」，可想而知，《古惑仔》電影系列在90年代轟動港台兩地，講述陳浩南人生的起跌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190312/59359344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190312%2F59359344&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6PUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=c2205887\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190312%2F59359344&h=98d5e617\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190312/59359344</a>"},{"pid":"3801515217a999b2b0be6d990af182dc4b26ba9f","tid":1057994,"uid":119223,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:57:55.000Z","msg":"The disappearing light is scattered in the wind"},{"pid":"18f320d2af719170fbb11ab74fd1446283da8ac0","tid":1057994,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:43:02.000Z","msg":"被韓國翻拍為《逃學威鳳》<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜嚟"},{"pid":"116ec202fa5fb5f76eb9ff98df11dbbc190590c0","tid":1057994,"uid":110832,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply